Package: vivlib
Title: An R package for useful bioinformatics wrappers
Version: 1.0.0
Author: Vivek Bhardwaj, <bhardwaj@ie-freiburg.mpg.de>
Maintainer: Vivek Bhardwaj, <bhardwaj@ie-freiburg.mpg.de>
Description: An R package for useful wrappers the are used quite often by me (vivekbhr) for my analysis.
